        <!-- Template-driven action creation -->
        <mxCell id="tmpl_create" value="&lt;b&gt;Create Actions from Templates&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:9px&quot;&gt;For each template × playbook:&lt;br&gt;1. Resolve playbook_ids (filter by associated)&lt;br&gt;2. Compute idempotency hash (incl. template_id)&lt;br&gt;3. Check dedup: find_by_idempotency_hash&lt;br&gt;4. Create ActionRecord with:&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; execution_mode, responsible_user/role&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; escalation_duration, evidence config&lt;br&gt;5. insert_action() → ActionStore (MongoDB)&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;align=left;spacingLeft=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
